      "created": "2018-04-12T18:01:30.801+0000",
      "description": "\r\nAs part of YARN-3895 ,  the timeline collector will enable storing the domain information in denormalized in the tables when security is enabled. \r\n\r\nThe collector would need to maintain a map in memory for app id to domain id & info and append this to entities while writing. \r\n\r\nIn case the collector goes down, this map is to be repopulated which is part of YARN-8089\r\n",
